frameDefinitions: This frame contains words that describe specific aspects of a Color.
There is a gradable amount of light in a particular Location.
An Entity is obscure, unnotable, and in general little-known.
An Astronomical_entity comes into view above the horizon as part of a regular, periodic process of (apparent) motion of the Astronomical_entity across the sky.
An Entity changes from a Prior_state to a Post_state in a sequence that follows a pre-defined plan, expectation, or model of change.
A Self_mover leaves an initial Source location.
frameExamples: The small print was bearly readable by the light of the very <t>dim</t> torch.
Geoffrey Rush was <t>little</t> <t>known</t> outside his native Australia when he soared to international prominence.
Venus <t>rose</t> at 5:23 AM, twenty minutes before the sun which reached the horizon at 5:43 AM.
Their offensive armament has <t>developed</t> from short range missiles to long-range ballistic weaponry in a relatively short period .
listRoleDefinitions: The color that is being described.
The entity whose <fen>Color</fen> is being described.
The place whose amout of light is being described.  The <fen>Location</fen> can also be a location in time, as seen in the second example below:
The entity from which the light eminates.
The <fen>Entity</fen> which is not widely known and rather obscure.
The <fen>Time</fen> during which the <fen>Entity</fen> is not well known.
The location where the <fen>Entity</fen> is not famous.
An entity which is periodically visible from the earth's surface.
This role identifies the <fen>Time</fen> when the <fen>Astronomical_entity</fen> appears.
This role identifies the <fen>Place</fen> from which the motion of the <fen>Astronomical_entity</fen> is viewed.
The time at which the progress occurs.
The location where the Progress occurs.
This is the entity which moves under its own power.

Any expression which implies a definite starting-point of motion expresses the frame element <fen>Source</fen>. In prepositional phrases, the prepositional object expresses the starting point of motion. In particles, the starting point of motion is understood from context.
The time at which the motion takes place.
The <fen>Place</fen> is where the motion (which is specified by a <fen>Source</fen>, <fen>Path</fen> or <fen>Goal</fen>) is located.
listRoleExamples: Fornalutx is a jewel of warm <fex>stone</fex>.
She hid from the man in a dark <fex>corner</fex>.
A dim <fex>lamp</fex> swung over the entrance to the castle.
Certain academic works are obscure <fex>only in North America</fex>.
Heku left one morning as <fex>the sun</fex> rose along the plain.
As the sun came up <fex>at 5:15 am</fex>, it made the red rocks almost glow.
The very end of the eclipse will be visible as the sun rises <fex>in some locations in Africa and northeastern North America</fex>.
Advances <fex>in marketing techniques</fex> have since rendered it obsolete.
<fex>When</fex> did the X-wing progress beyond the drawing board?
